<br>
Use your training points on Research. What else do you have to use it on? Trade skills are just a way to sap money from your bank account, your casting skills will increase with usage, and your melee skills are pathetic all the time.<br>
<br>
The drawbacks of using points are that you only get 5 per level (but the cap on research rises at that rate too) and that it costs you money. But I once spent 100 plat at level 24 to pursue the practice research, and you don't get the guaranteed benefits of increasing your research skill.<br>
<br>
Use the guild trainer, what else have you got to spend it on? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> ICEHOUES</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(9/19/00 7:49:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   CAN U HELP ME OUT???</span><hr size=1> I AM NEW AT USING MY MAGE.  I AM LEL 15 NOW AND WILL BE LEL 16 SOON.  I DO NOT REALLY UNDERSTAND HOW TO DO RECEAECH.  I KNOW YOU HAVE TO FIND WORD AND COMBIND THEM, BUT THAT IS ALL I REALLY KNOW.  IF U CAN, CAN U PLEAES EXPLAIN HOW TO START DOING RESERECH. <br>
